modName: Naruto Kuchiyose no Jutsu Kyodaina kani
summary:
Summon a Giant Mudcrab. With Naruto Sound effects.
<br/><br/>Requires all DLC's
descriptionHtml:
This mod was made because I am a naruto fan and I was messing around in the Creation Kit. I liked the mod so much that I thought "Hey I should share this with others" Thus the Naruto Kuchiyose no Jutsu Kyodaina kani was born. Don't expect very many updates unless you enjoy the mod and let me know so I can possibly add dialouge to the crab. Who knows, Leave your comments and let me know if you want to see more summoning jutsu mods.

Summons a giant Mudcrab with naruto summoning Jutsu sound effects. For this version the spell can be bought from the merchant in the riverwood trader. 
Updates coming soon!
author: jdblake508
